    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener><salute>Dear Sir</salute></opener>
                <p>Y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> kind Letters &amp; pacquet from <placeName ref="pl0316">Dundee</placeName> came safely; I am much obliged to you for them but in
                    this place have not time to cast my eye over them. I am busy getting materials
                    for a <bibl type="authorial"><title ref="bi0209">map of Scotland</title></bibl> if you
                    know of any Surveys or Charts that will be of use pray acquaint me. I mean at
                    <placeName ref="pl0076">Edinburgh</placeName> for I know what may be had here. is
                    <bibl type="authorial"><title ref="bi0145">Briceâ€™s Survey of the coast of
                            Strathnavern</title></bibl> to be had with you.</p>
                <p>Be so good as to leave the Letter for <persName ref="pe0203">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Mackenzie</persName> at his house &amp; put the other in the
                    post. I stay here only till the 11<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> of next month.
                    Pray did you ever send the prints to <persName ref="pe0114">D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Saunders</persName> for He writes as if he had not got them.
                    <persName ref="pe0026">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> White</persName> has but
                    just had my order from <persName ref="pe0180">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                        Balfour</persName>.</p>
                <closer><salute>I am Dear Sir <lb/>y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> most obed<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> Serv<hi rend="superscript">t</hi></salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="pe0232">Tho. Pennant</persName></signed>
                    <placeName ref="pl0699">London</placeName>
                <dateline>Dec<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> 29<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>
                    1774</dateline></closer>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p><address>
                        <addrLine>M<hi rend="superscript">r.</hi> Paton,</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Custom House</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Edinburg</addrLine>
                    </address>
                </p>
                <p>Free <lb/><persName ref="pe0243">Ph: Yorke</persName></p>


                <p><stamp type="frank">FREE</stamp></p>

                <p><stamp type="handstamp">29<lb/>DE</stamp></p>
                <p><stamp type="handstamp">29<lb/>DE</stamp></p>
            </div>
        </body>
